headline: Prediction: 3 Stocks That Will Be Worth More Than Palantir Technologies 5 Years From Now
summary: Intuitive Surgical is smaller than Palantir, but could be the bigger winner by the end of the decade.  Alibaba could widen its market cap gap with Palantir thanks to artificial intelligence (AI) tailwinds.  Google parent Alphabet's challenges shouldn't diminish its current huge size advantage over Palantir.
